00:38:24.035 --> 00:38:46.455
I was growing great taproots with you.'I said, 'What do you mean?'He said, 'You're freaking out because of all the fruit and all that I've done and how everything has happened so quickly, but it took years of cultivation that nobody saw. There were great roots that I've had growing way down deep.

00:38:46.456 --> 00:39:06.199
