00:42:41.980 --> 00:42:47.891
I know that's a lot of something, but I tried to tell you the process because this is all so interesting to me.

00:42:47.892 --> 00:43:06.396
Over the last three years—it'll be three years in June—of just growing, and now we reach millions and millions of people for Jesus every month. Millions, literally. All glory to God.

00:43:06.397 --> 00:43:41.556
Then Facebook contacted us today and said, 'We want to discuss things with you over the phone.'I said, 'I don't want to talk to you.'It was funny because they banned me, and then one of their big people reached out to us and said, 'We want to talk to you over the phone about some of the things you're posting and if you want to be reinstated back on our platform.'I think the whole thing is interesting because I was just like, 'What do they want to say to us over the phone?'But we'll talk to them and we'll go back on Facebook.

00:43:41.557 --> 00:43:53.479
